You can create a class that encapsulates the data you care about. Something like this:

```
class MyText {
  String message;
  int x;
  int y;

  public MyText(String message, int x, int y) {
    this.message = message;
    this.x = x;
    this.y = y;
  }

  void draw(){
    text(message, x, y);
  }
}
```

